title: enterprisegrade
extract: Answered Feb 6, 2013. If the context of "Enterprise Grade" is product literature, it's a marketing term simply mean that it will work for an enterprise, usually it can be scaled to a large number of users to to satisfy mission critical tasks. Thank you for your feedback! Your feedback is private.
